Gorox
=====

  Gorox is the server and its control agent.

Process Architecture
====================

  There are two kinds of gorox processes: leader and worker.
  There are two process architectures:

    * 1 leader + 1 worker, worker has GOMAXPROCS=N
	* 1 leader + N workers, each worker has GOMAXPROCS=1

